        <title>I've vetted 47 peptide suppliers. Only 4 passed — and four reasons why most fail. — The Operator Brief</title>
        <meta name="description" content="A founder's four-flag framework for vetting a research-peptide supplier: the COA, the purity number, the batch match, the track record. None of the four is price.">
